{
  "local_port": 34278,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I print an application form on the OJAS website?",
  "response": "To print an application form from the **OJAS (Online Job Application System)** website, follow these steps:\n\n### Steps to Print an Application Form on OJAS:\n1. **Visit the OJAS Website**:\n   - Go to the official OJAS website: [https://ojas.gujarat.gov.in](https://ojas.gujarat.gov.in).\n\n2. **Log In**:\n   - If you already have an account, log in using your **Username** and **Password**.\n   - If you don\u2019t have an account, register first by clicking on the **\u201cNew Registration\u201d** link.\n\n3. **Find the Job Advertisement**:\n   - Navigate to the **\u201cAdvertisement\u201d** section and search for the job you\u2019re interested in.\n   - Click on the job advertisement to view the details.\n\n4. **Apply for the Job**:\n   - Click on the **\u201cApply Online\u201d** button for the specific job.\n   - Fill in the required details in the application form.\n\n5. **Preview and Submit**:\n   - After filling out the form, preview your application to ensure all details are correct.\n   - Submit the application.\n\n6. **Download/Print the Application**:\n   - After submission, you will see an option to **\"Save as PDF\"** or **\"Print Application\"**.\n   - Click on **\u201cPrint Application\u201d** to directly print the form or **\u201cSave as PDF\u201d** to download it for printing later.\n\n7. **Print the Form**:\n   - If you saved the form as a PDF, open the file and print it using your printer.\n   - If you chose \"Print Application,\" follow the on-screen instructions to print the form.\n\n### Important Notes:\n- Ensure you have a stable internet connection while filling out and submitting the form.\n- Keep the printout for future reference, especially for any further stages of the recruitment process.\n- If you face any technical issues, contact the OJAS helpdesk or refer to the **\u201cHelp Manual\u201d** available on the website.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to successfully print your application form from the OJAS website.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
